   University of Puerto Rico; International Institute of Tropical
   Forestry-USDA Forest Service. Forero-Montana; Office of the Dean of
   Graduate Studies and Research, University of Puerto Rico},
Funding-Text = {We thank Maria Aponte-Pagan, Raina Dominguez, Zara Dowling, Maria
   Moskalenko, and Nereida Ramirez for their helpful assistance with this
   project. We thank Chelse Prather, Nicholas Brokaw, Chris Nytch, and two
